snippet.textDisplay:
I know that this song is about being in an toxic, on & off relationship that one person forces themselves to stay in just bec of love; but to me it's speaks largely something that my current healed self would say to, my old self who spent years hating herself bec she thought the way she is somehow isn't enough.

Now how I have come to love myself the way I am, the present me hates that past me that's didn't love herself enough and wasted so many years hating herself for nothing.

Not many would get this, but to whoever does and is going through something that I've been through, you are enough & and you are stronger than you think.

And thanks to Selena for creating such an amazing song. o((*^▽^*))o
